      "review_summary": "This PR changes Control UI `clearSubmittedComposerState` so sending always clears `host.chatMessage` and `host.chatAttachments` instead of only clearing when the submitted draft and attachments still match.\n\nPR surface: Source -1. Total -1 across 1 file.\n\nReproducibility: yes. at source level. The delayed model-switch send path reaches this helper before the request completes, and existing tests show newer draft or attachment edits must survive that wait.",
